==模板介紹==
This will create a reference link to a basketball player's statistics page on http://www.basketball-reference.com.

==參數及使用方法==
This template requires 3 parameters:
*'''name''', the name of the player on the title of the references basketball-reference.com page
*'''id''', the identifier after "players/" and before ".html" in the url to the statistics page. 
*'''date''', the date the page was accessed.

==範例==
For a reference to Kareem Abdul-Jabbar's page at http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/a/abdulka01.html:

<pre>
{{Cite basketball-reference |name=Kareem Abdul-Jabbar|id=a/abdulka01 |date=March 26, 2012}}</pre>
Output:
{{Cite basketball-reference |name=Kareem Abdul-Jabbar|id=a/abdulka01 | date=March 26, 2012}}

